content":"你說得沒錯","from":240.97,"location":2,"to":242.77},{"content":"反正 如果你改變想法了 就隨時聯繫我","from":243.26,"location":2,"to":246.53},{"content":"價格方面也可以再商榷哦","from":248.34,"location":2,"to":250.38},{"content":"沒這個必要 放棄吧","from":250.38,"location":2,"to":252.2},{"content":"問題在於報酬嗎","from":255.87,"location":2,"to":257.4},{"content":"不是！","from":257.4,"location":2,"to":258.34},{"content":"我們願意提供更高的待遇","from":258.64,"location":2,"to":260.51},{"content":"不需要！","from":260.67,"location":2,"to":261.67},{"content":"破例授予你爵位","from":262.47,"location":2,"to":264.45},{"content":"我拒絕！","from":264.59,"location":2,"to":265.94},{"content":"想找男人可以考慮我家兒子","from":266.05,"location":2,"to":267.8},{"content":"你在說什麼鬼話！","from":267.8,"location":2,"to":269.75},{"content":"真是的 你們鬧夠了沒有！","from":270.33,"location":2,"to":272.19},{"content":"我在雷德這裡簽下了終身雇傭契約","from":272.22,"location":2,"to":275.25},{"content":"以後不會當冒險者了！","from":275.38,"location":2,"to":277.31},{"content":"如果你們敢為難雷德 讓他離開這裡的話","from":279.06,"location":2,"to":283.32},{"content":"我也會和他一起離開！","from":283.32,"location":2,"to":285.46},{"content":"你都聽到了嗎","from":292.43,"location":2,"to":293.54},{"content":"在我這裡 簽了終身雇傭契約…","from":294.33,"location":2,"to":298.77},{"content":"那個 你在生氣嗎","from":299.28,"location":2,"to":301.37},{"content":"因為他們太囉嗦","from":301.86,"location":2,"to":303.34},{"content":"還一直說奇怪的話 我下意識就…","from":303.34,"location":2,"to":306.08},{"content":"莉特","from":306.2,"location":2,"to":306.77},{"content":"過來一下","from":307.8,"location":2,"to":308.31},{"content":"什麼","from":308.62,"location":2,"to":309.56},{"content":"那個…把手伸出來","from":310.9,"location":2,"to":313.76},{"content":"嗯？","from":315.88,"location":2,"to":316.76},{"content":"雷德？","from":318.25,"location":2,"to":319.55},{"content":"送你的禮物","from":322.12,"location":2,"to":322.94},{"content":"終身雇傭契約的訂金","from":325.05,"location":2,"to":327.29},{"content":"琥珀手環","from":330.85,"location":2,"to":332.63},{"content":"這個…","from":333.0,"location":2,"to":333.77},{"content":"是訂金哦","from":33