":2,"to":1275.14},{"content":"我知道 你失去了哥哥會感到不安","from":1276.4,"location":2,"to":1279.36},{"content":"雖然你是勇者 但你也是一個普通的女孩子","from":1279.58,"location":2,"to":1283.5},{"content":"和吉迪恩相比","from":1284.46,"location":2,"to":1285.9},{"content":"我陪你渡過的時間雖然比較短","from":1286.59,"location":2,"to":1289.78},{"content":"但我無論何時都是你的同伴","from":1290.37,"location":2,"to":1293.39},{"content":"就是這個人 把哥哥給…","from":1294.46,"location":2,"to":1296.19},{"content":"抱歉","from":1311.36,"location":2,"to":1312.45},{"content":"勇者必須繼續旅行","from":1314.38,"location":2,"to":1316.83},{"content":"因為 我是勇者","from":1319.13,"location":2,"to":1322.9},{"content":"但我現在","from":1323.84,"location":2,"to":1325.77},{"content":"哥哥成分不足","from":1327.2,"location":2,"to":1328.58},{"content":"在最高層被救下了","from":1330.97,"location":2,"to":1335.44},{"content":"誕生在永恆的星球上","from":1335.57,"location":2,"to":1341.21},{"content":"背對著逐漸模糊的景色","from":1354.27,"location":2,"to":1358.56},{"content":"試著開始了生活","from":1358.61,"location":2,"to":1363.53},{"content":"收集 再失去","from":1363.54,"location":2,"to":1368.17},{"content":"打開身旁的窗戶","from":1368.4,"location":2,"to":1373.27},{"content":"「回憶增加了嗎?」","from":1373.44,"location":2,"to":1378.56},{"content":"不要死腦筋啦","from":1378.79,"location":2,"to":1381.65},{"content":"大膽走出來吧","from":1381.67,"location":2,"to":1384.16},{"content":"你會創造出來的","from":1384.66,"location":2,"to":1389.31},{"content":"最終觸碰的","from":1392.22,"location":2,"to":1397.28},{"content":"那個奇蹟","from":1397.54,"location":2,"to":1399.22},{"content":"我們來聊聊吧","from":1399.22,"location":2,"to":1402.11},{"content":"從未設想過的景色","from":1403.07,"location":2,"to":1407.9},{"content":"將填滿你的世界","from":1407.97,"location":2,"to":1413.37}]}